section.section:
The Commission consists of 13 members appointed by the Governor with the advice and consent of the Senate. Of the members:
Each shall be qualified to deal with the matters within the authority of the Commission;
Six shall be volunteer emergency services personnel or instructors;
Three shall be emergency services instructors who are career personnel representing the academies;
Three shall be career emergency services personnel who are not instructors; and
One shall be a member of the general public.
